{2000}{}{I sure hope it rains soon.@@Our crops are dying from lack of water.@@Even the wells have gone dry.@@Not a cloud in the sky.@@I'm thinking of moving away from here.@@Modoc used to be a prosperous farming community.@@Life in Modoc is slow. Just the way I like it.@@I hear that people have seen glowing figures during the night hours at the Ghost Farm.@@Did you hear? They found some idiot to go and investigate the Ghost Farm.@@I've been to the Ghost Farm. Scary!@@Daytime is the best time to go to the Ghost Farm.@@Karl used to live at the Ghost Farm. Now he probably haunts it.@@People shouldn't mess with the supernatural.@@Why would ghosts grow food?}
{3000}{}{They found out the people living at the Ghost Farm call themselves Slags.@@What kind of name is Slag?@@I don't trust the Slags.@@Maybe I could trust the Slags if I knew what happened to Karl.@@Did you hear? A powerful priest exorcised the ghosts from the farm.@@The harvest from the Ghost Farm should keep us fed for another year.@@There's not a drop of water at the Ghost Farm.Maybe the soil at the Ghost Farm is magic. How else could the crops grow without water?@@Maybe the ghosts used blood to feed their crops.@@I think the ghosts were stealing our water.@@I bet things will return to normal around here, now that the ghosts are gone.}

